myVelibCore.utilities

Class Time

  • java.lang.Object
    • myVelibCore.utilities.Time

  • public class Time
extends java.lang.Object
    This class allows to have a clock, simulating a time that is running out.

    There is an actual time that is the same for all users and that is updated regularly

    Author:
    Edouard Benauw & Simon Lecler
